      "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/git/commits/76e63c36dc524da8682b8b18d07ce78d027122a4",
      "actor": null,
      "commit_id": null,
      "commit_url": null,
      "created_at": null,
      "html_url": "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/76e63c36dc524da8682b8b18d07ce78d027122a4",
      "tree": {
        "sha": "6cd111153c382339fdbde0c20ff70e7133afee30",
        "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/git/trees/6cd111153c382339fdbde0c20ff70e7133afee30"
      },
      "verification": {
        "verified": true,
        "reason": "valid",
        "payload": "tree 6cd111153c382339fdbde0c20ff70e7133afee30\nparent 0fb5e167e8e332e3d40659406b3222a22747aa0e\nauthor Cory Fields <cory-nospam-@coryfields.com> 1777399236 +0000\ncommitter fanquake <fanquake@gmail.com> 1777539082 +0100\n\nmulti_index: fix compilation failure with boost >= 1.91\n\nThis effectively reverts a3cb309e7c31853f272bffaa65fb6ab0a7cc4083 from PR #30194.\n\nThat PR reduced the multi_index type signatures as recommended upstream, but\nthis is no longer supported as of boost 1.91 because it is no longer necessary.\n1.91 drops support for the pre-c++11 work-arounds that bloated the type\nsignatures to begin with.\n\nThe upstream `BOOST_MULTI_INDEX_ENABLE_MPL_SUPPORT` define is meant to provide\ncompatibility with removed features, but it does not work for this case. Using\n`indexed_by` directly when defining the `multi_index` (as opposed to inheriting\nfrom it) works with all versions, and avoids the use of the back-compat define.\n\nThis is a slight regression when building against boost < 1.91 because the\nbloated type signatures are reintroduced in that case, but it's not significant\nenough to go to the trouble of introducing version detection and ifdefs.\n\nGithub-Pull: #35175\nRebased-From: 0bc9d354dfd8074d1c36a891a69b6585a8775c65\n",
        "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niQJPBAABCAA5FiEEz7FuIclQ9n+pXlWPLuufXMCVJsEFAmnzGAobFIAAAAAABAAO\nbWFudTIsMi41KzEuMTIsMCwzAAoJEC7rn1zAlSbB5wsP/Ak+StebMoWKQ6BaxODx\n3dD2JxEZ7Ss+Y3TXfx2rI0dEafAGDq0qv2+pfmqr1Mi9y6GYw3RJEPX2+4+nPHbM\neY5i0s3S3FKLSdOf+pDI2W1oFFXvnQqt5VYFcEz/kCjvzQczlOqWCU99VEBtb/dc\njQstAljCwbkue1vtz7YdUvvMlW9K61f/CxPZHm5PxkwsD1IzSJSZkiFf/wRryRKB\nzsf91DFj+UtP3xkCLXJeOD9krK8LMGRiSzU8ZscTFqx6mSFgXyWPMysLy+oys2gV\nkW+JJpMDS6Y7XRZt8S2tiXYdqxdfAL8G6ISHb4CbmvWsl47bDT+HmbnwdOiLISHi\nR7rd0sgxk0ZmLD/77fSjv1sfqJ0oWrnlwVswWPN/Bw7HFXDvjvV8PaWfCaIiylYg\ndJmVGmOTaR5yZaq1U0/DuSSVbscTZq9BhtJ6H/lQjuuQeQgu1950NHVtcuvjs87i\nGf/c4JzYose7j3l/LZJVEKZgpSb6sZt+Y6P5Yg2iYxMRol/chbcElh1YRvvM4Am3\nmzLYFdnCAl3M9vFYz1vij9AAvUxQ5srO7i2PajMvMB9snu7RPw+PSrisC3FAFss2\nJTH0no/UeN6UEn1sg7SnadQK5KYBxs3jN561dpqgsFzEMW+wAOMftSZPUyztbdKd\naY/hI+gfcUJx9wjwykjNDM15\n=ugh/\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----"
